Index.title: Hello world!
Index.elevateYourExperience: Elevate your delivery experience with us.
Index.elevateYourExperienceText: Cover your business`s day-to-day needs with with our service, ensuring you never run out of the basics.
Index.chooseFromCategories: Choose from a wide range of products
Index.weOfferText: Simplify office logistics with our monthly deliveries
Index.feature1Text: No more last minute runs to the store or overpaying for office supplies
Index.feature2Text: We work with the best suppliers to ensure you get the best products every month
Index.feature3Text: We provide special offers on an extensive selection of products
Index.feature4Text: We provide customizable delivery schedules and payment alternatives.
Index.cancelSubscriptionTime: When can I cancel my subscription?
Index.cancelSubscriptionTimeText: You can cancel your subscription at any time. However, if you cancel your subscription 3 days before the next delivery date, you will still receive the next delivery.
Index.howToPayForSubscription: How can I pay for my subscription?
Index.howToPayForSubscriptionText: Currently we only accept payment via bank transfer(Humo and UzCard) or cash on delivery.
Index.howCanChangeDeliveryAddress: How can I change my delivery address?
Index.howCanChangeDeliveryAddressText: You can change your delivery address by going to your profile -> delivery location and changing the delivery address.
Index.howCanIChangeDeliveryDate: How can I change the delivery date?
Index.howCanIChangeDeliveryDateText: You can change the delivery date by going to your profile and changing the delivery date.
Index.howCanIChangeQuantity: How can I change quantity of the products in the subscription?
Index.howCanIChangeQuantityText: You can change the quantity of the products in the subscription by going to your order and changing the quantity of the products on the list.
